{"tid":1457402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"走同唔走係自己決定，唔好再理引戰狗","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:31:26.000Z","uid":229880,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c02fd8c5dae64aa5345c61332d60b37076fbdf1b","tid":1457402,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:39:38.000Z","msg":"都兩個幾月啦<br />\n每次突發事情都一定係訊息亂傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本即時係fact check唔到。貼唔貼證都無用，因為對家一樣可以貼證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯一可靠可信係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己驚、承受唔到就走，頂得順唔驚就留<br />\n<br />\n事實上，走唔走呢兩班人無衝突，亦唔駛互屌，我都相信無<br />\n<br />\n但係，出面嘅post明顯有班人係咁引戰<br />\n<br />\n大家請警惕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無聊今日走唔走，都請注意安全<br />\n就算一陣係點，今日已經成功左第一次<br />\n<br />\n無必要互屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e0e6e7d7ea062cf238d60b0f624f072a46df9e","tid":1457402,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推"},{"pid":"1b6548cea590106318c7c3f94e83ff42766bca59","tid":1457402,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n